<h1>Shuttle Private Bus Service Guatemala Antigua</h1><p>&nbsp;Casa Xelajú provides reliable and safe private shuttle services throughout Guatemala, offering transportation from Quetzaltenango (Xela) to destinations such as Lake Atitlán, Panajachel, Antigua, Chichicastenango, and La Aurora International Airport in Guatemala City. Since 1987, Casa Xelajú has been a trusted provider for tourists, students, and business travelers seeking stress-free, efficient transport. Their fleet includes private cars for three passengers and minibuses accommodating up to 25 passengers, making it suitable for solo travelers, families, and larger groups.</p>
