<p>&nbsp;The service is designed with flexibility in mind, offering customizable pickup and drop-off times to match travelers’ itineraries. Bilingual staff assist throughout the journey, ensuring a smooth and convenient travel experience. Daily departures are available from Quetzaltenango to various destinations, and the company maintains a 24-hour presence at Guatemala City’s Aurora Airport. For travelers requiring overnight stays in Guatemala City, Casa Xelajú offers homestay with local families, including continental breakfast and convenient transport to the bus station the following day.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Casa Xelajú’s shuttle services cater to multiple destinations, including Antigua, Lake Atitlán, Panajachel, IRTRA, Chichicastenango, and Las Georginas, as well as airport transfers between Quetzaltenango and Guatemala City. For larger groups, the company provides minibuses and private buses accommodating 9, 15, or 25 passengers, making it ideal for school trips, tours, and organized excursions. Pricing is based on group size and vehicle type, and reservations are recommended in advance to secure your preferred schedule.</p>
<p>&nbsp;With decades of experience, a variety of vehicle options, flexible schedules, and English-speaking staff, Casa Xelajú ensures that private transportation across Guatemala is safe, comfortable, and reliable. Their long-standing reputation since 1987 reflects consistent customer satisfaction, making them a preferred choice for travelers seeking dependable shuttle services.</p><a href="https://www.casaxelaju.com/shuttle-service-private-transportation-guatemala/"><b><span style="font-size: x-large;">Shuttle Private Bus Service Guatemala Antigua</span></b></a><br />
